The low wages, the lowest wages in all of Mexico, come to unemployment and black labour, according to the statistics of the Instituto Mexicano del Seguro Social (Mexican Social Insurance Institute) and the Secretaryía del Trabajo y Previsión Social (Government Office for Employment and Social Care in Mexico).
